                    <span>These movies are the best I have seen. Even though some of the characters in the books are not in the films, it's still worth watching all three. I have read the books a few times and have seen the films like 15 times each. The extended editions are great because they fill in the blanks and answer questions that the cut versions leave. I love the LOTR trilogy, both the books and the films!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Greatest movie ever!!!!</div>
